_sText: This is a remake of my map gg_woods. As you can see it is highly modified. It features: -Custom Soundscape -Custom Textures -Custom Skybox -Custom Models -Custom Music -Color Correction -Edit nav file with area names -32 Spawns CREDITS Gift boxes and Xmas tree by Mr.Kit Custom tree and bush models by unknown Jingle Bells music by Kevin Macleod (incompetech.com) Wood textures from www.grsites.com Level Design, skybox texture, normal maps for the textures and FPSB promo texture by me Original FPSB Logo made by it's respective creators at fpsbanana.com Many thanks to Nayor for his help. The filesize of the bsp if 30 MB so I would suggest you to use this map on your server only if you have fast download. This map works on normal servers too since it has buyzones. I wish you Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year! HAVE FUN!
